    <h1>Managing bank details</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>On this page of the manual, you learn how to save your <a href="/en/payment/managing-bank-details#10">own bank details</a> and your <a href="/en/payment/managing-bank-details#63">customers' bank details</a> as well as how to set up <a href="/en/payment/managing-bank-details#70">EBICS</a> and <a href="/en/payment/managing-bank-details#200">SEPA</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="10">1. Saving own bank details</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The bank details that you save in the basic settings will be linked within the entire system. Corrections to the bank details only have to be made in this one menu. The changes will go into effect for the entire system.</p>
</div>
