<h2 id="63">2. Saving the customer’s bank details</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can save the customer’s bank details in the <strong>Settings</strong> tab of a customer’s data record or delete them again as needed. Bank details are needed, e.g. for the payment method <a href="/en/payment/managing-payment-methods#40">debit</a>. There is also an <a href="/en/payment/beta-managing-payments#intable-import-customer-bank-data">import function</a> for bank details in plentymarkets. Contact a legal adviser for information about the current laws in your own country as well as in other countries of delivery.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Saving the customer’s bank details:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
